query:
SELECT e.name as employeeName, e.code as employeeCode, 
       SUM(er.total) as totalRevenue,
       COUNT(er.id) as daysCount,
       GROUP_CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(dr.date, '%Y-%m-%d')) as dates
FROM employeeRevenues er
JOIN dailyRevenues dr ON er.dailyRevenueId = dr.id
JOIN employees e ON er.employeeId = e.id
WHERE dr.date >= '2026-01-01' AND dr.date <= '2026-01-07'
GROUP BY e.id, e.name, e.code
ORDER BY totalRevenue DESC;
